Privacy Policy for Sequence Strikers

Effective Date: [Date]

Introduction:
Welcome to Sequence Strikers! We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal data. This privacy policy will inform you how we handle your personal data when you play our game and tell you about your privacy rights.

1. Information We Collect:

Data Provided by You: This includes data entered when creating an account, such as your username and email address.
Data Collected Automatically: We automatically collect certain data when you access and use our game, including your gameplay data, achievements, and technical data like your IP address and device characteristics.
2. How We Use Your Data:

To Provide and Manage the Game: We use your data to operate and manage your access to the game, including tracking your progress and providing game support.
To Improve Our Game: We analyze gameplay data to enhance game features and user experience.
To Communicate With You: We use your contact information to send you game updates and respond to your inquiries.
3. Sharing Your Data:
We do not share your personal data with third parties, except when required by law or to provide necessary game functions, such as cloud hosting services.

4. Data Security:
We implement appropriate security measures to protect against unauthorized access to or alteration of your data.

5. Your Rights:
You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal data. You can also object to the processing of your data and request data portability where applicable.

6. Changes to This Policy:
We may update this policy from time to time. The updated version will be indicated by an updated “Effective Date” and the updated version will be effective as soon as it is accessible.

Contact Us:
If you have any questions about this policy, please contact us at niv@starbeam.games
